<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><title>Rent Agreement</title></head>
<body>
  <h1 style="text-align: center;">Residential Lease Agreement</h1>

  <p>This Lease Agreement is entered into on <strong>{{date}}</strong> between <strong>{{landlord}}</strong> ("Landlord") residing at <strong>{{landlordAddress}}</strong> and <strong>{{tenant}}</strong> ("Tenant") residing at <strong>{{tenantAddress}}</strong>.</p>

  <h3>1. Property</h3>
  <p>The Landlord agrees to rent to the Tenant the property located at <strong>{{propertyAddress}}</strong>.</p>

  <h3>2. Term</h3>
  <p>The lease term shall begin on <strong>{{startDate}}</strong> and end on <strong>{{endDate}}</strong>.</p>

  <h3>3. Rent</h3>
  <p>The monthly rent shall be ₹<strong>{{monthlyRent}}</strong>, payable in advance by the 5th of each month.</p>

  <h3>4. Security Deposit</h3>
  <p>The Tenant agrees to pay a refundable security deposit of ₹<strong>{{securityDeposit}}</strong> before moving in.</p>

  <h3>5. Maintenance</h3>
  <p>The Tenant shall maintain the property in good condition and will not cause damage beyond normal wear and tear.</p>

  <h3>6. Governing Law</h3>
  <p>This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of <strong>{{governingLaw}}</strong>.</p>

  <br />
  <p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, both parties have executed this Lease Agreement.</p>

  <br /><br />
  <p><strong>Landlord:</strong> {{landlord}}</p>
  <p><strong>Tenant:</strong> {{tenant}}</p>
</body>
</html>
